{"tid":1249023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家放料千祁千祈唔好加密","createTime":"2019-06-21T15:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:05:58.000Z","uid":45979,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2e8e60bb1378b4a5548abeacb02603d85ae492","tid":1249023,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"致各位連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n首先今日辛苦曬，發掘到新社運模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到而家咁夜仲留實屬不智，我地在明敵在暗，我強烈建議而家即刻散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終烏燈黑火有咩事記者未必即刻影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋好重要一件事：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>因為有好多好多出咗嚟嘅手足本身係CD ROM，我地放料又好咩都好，千萬千萬唔好加密啊！加密咗就全部冇ac嘅仲曬伏</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔需要驚有狗會睇到，因為根本冇得避，佢地入面一定有人有AC，而我真係唔相信冇ac但係Mon po嘅狗會多過CD ROM義士。而且下面留言人多口雜，分分鐘啲三毛入曬嚟帶風向，搞分化，然後大家無所適從，畀人逐個擊破，咁你為玩膠搞到咁就真係唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以為多數人利益<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好仲諗住玩膠，千祈唔好加密啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"536bfae7ea82816c612c2aafd2ebf25beb7ea97f","tid":1249023,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67f50bb6e3c8918c7a8a2e97ed1fbcf23d620ee","tid":1249023,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:19:45.000Z","msg":"push push"},{"pid":"64f33f6ba254ce98f33ddf1e7fca36d43bf8f984","tid":1249023,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"c146b3937210793adabdbd693f2b21054976daab","tid":1249023,"uid":13490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f90d1363b9fe46169c3f62d1af9bffb80abf3d5","tid":1249023,"uid":4